{"tid":2510273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大團隊發現輸入個案帶有印度雙重變種病毒株","createTime":"2021-04-30T04:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T05:01:25.000Z","uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20baabaa13c66e4f91116738d9dcdfa46bc46a17","tid":2510273,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433028&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433028%26home%3D1&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=cc5e81e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433028%26home%3D1&h=418ca01a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433028&amp;home=1</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】理工大學的團隊首次發現，在本港的新冠病毒的輸入確診個案中，帶有印度雙重變種病毒株。<br />\n<br />\n理工大學醫療及科技資料學系研究團隊在最新的新冠病毒基因排序發現，數宗由印度抵港的輸入個案帶有印度雙重變種病毒株，驗出E484Q及L452R突變，大部分個案來自本月4日由印度新德里抵港的UK6395航班。"},{"pid":"ec94351df123df6a9306f5085a340abb2eb7bdd1","tid":2510273,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3Nmhbg.jpg&amp;h=4ec9fa31&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"b91e509361bcde3a4e78f93e35fc99ba3208889d","tid":2510273,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"封印度未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd13ed7096274123594ea9507c57a19a1f5b545","tid":2510273,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b91e509361bcde3a4e78f93e35fc99ba3208889d","tid":2510273,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime